{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Academic Validation Suite\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates how the `stats-transformer` library replicates data processing from major macroeconomic papers. We compare our library's output against the researchers' original datasets."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "sys.path.append(\"..\")\n",
    "from src.stats_transformer.featurization.feature_engineering import FeatureEngineer"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Nakamura & Steinsson (2018)\n",
    "**Logic:** First-differencing of daily nominal yields.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Step 1.1: Raw Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = Path(\"../data/examples/Nakamura_Steinsson_2018\")\n",
    "df_raw = pd.read_csv(data_dir / \"NominalYields.csv\")\n",
    "df_raw.rename(columns={df_raw.columns[0]: \"date\", \"SVENY01\": \"NY1\"}, inplace=True)\n",
    "df_raw[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df_raw[\"date\"])\n",
    "df_raw[\"country\"] = \"USA\"\n",
    "df_raw.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 1.2: Ground Truth (Stata Master Dataset)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_gt = pd.read_stata(data_dir / \"master.dta\")\n",
    "df_gt[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df_gt[\"date_daily\"])\n",
    "df_gt[[\"date\", \"DNY1\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 1.3: Stats-Transformer Transformation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "engineer = FeatureEngineer(\n",
    "    transformations=[\"changeraw\"],\n",
    "    entity_column=\"country\",\n",
    "    date_column=\"date\",\n",
    "    period=\"daily\",\n",
    "    data_columns=[\"NY1\"],\n",
    "    verbose=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "df_lib = engineer.fit_transform(df_raw)\n",
    "df_lib[[\"date\", \"NY1\", \"NY1_changeraw\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 1.4: Comparison and Error Calculation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "merged = pd.merge(df_lib[[\"date\", \"NY1_changeraw\"]], df_gt[[\"date\", \"DNY1\"]], on=\"date\")\n",
    "merged[\"absolute_error\"] = (merged[\"NY1_changeraw\"] - merged[\"DNY1\"]).abs()\n",
    "merged.dropna().sort_values(\"absolute_error\", ascending=False).head(10)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Bauer & Swanson (2023)\n",
    "**Logic:** Log-Difference of Nonfarm Payrolls.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Step 2.1: Raw Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = Path(\"../data/examples/Bauer_Swanson_2023\")\n",
    "df_nfp = pd.read_csv(data_dir / \"NonfarmPayrolls.txt\", sep=r\"\\s+\", header=None, names=[\"year\", \"month\", \"value\"])\n",
    "df_nfp[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df_nfp[\"year\"].astype(str) + \"-\" + df_nfp[\"month\"].astype(str) + \"-01\")\n",
    "df_nfp[\"country\"] = \"USA\"\n",
    "df_nfp.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 2.2: Stats-Transformer Transformation (Log + Diff)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "eng_log = FeatureEngineer(transformations=[\"log\"], entity_column=\"country\", date_column=\"date\", data_columns=[\"value\"], verbose=False)\n",
    "df_log = eng_log.fit_transform(df_nfp)\n",
    "\n",
    "eng_diff = FeatureEngineer(transformations=[\"changeraw\"], entity_column=\"country\", date_column=\"date\", data_columns=[\"value_log\"], verbose=False)\n",
    "df_lib = eng_diff.fit_transform(df_log)\n",
    "df_lib[[\"date\", \"value\", \"value_log\", \"value_log_changeraw\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 2.3: Comparison with Manual Logic"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_manual = df_nfp.copy()\n",
    "df_manual[\"target\"] = np.log(df_manual[\"value\"]).diff()\n",
    "\n",
    "merged = pd.merge(df_lib, df_manual[[\"date\", \"target\"]], on=\"date\")\n",
    "merged[[\"date\", \"value_log_changeraw\", \"target\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Bauer, Bernanke, & Milstein (2023)\n",
    "**Logic:** Pct Change and Raw Difference.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Step 3.1: Raw Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = Path(\"../data/examples/BBM_2023\")\n",
    "df_bbm = pd.read_csv(data_dir / \"feds_subset.csv\", skiprows=9)\n",
    "df_bbm[\"Date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df_bbm[\"Date\"])\n",
    "df_bbm[\"country\"] = \"USA\"\n",
    "for col in [\"SVENY01\", \"SVENY10\"]:\n",
    "    df_bbm[col] = pd.to_numeric(df_bbm[col], errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "df_bbm = df_bbm.dropna(subset=[\"SVENY01\", \"SVENY10\"])\n",
    "df_bbm[[\"Date\", \"SVENY01\", \"SVENY10\"]].head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 3.2: Stats-Transformer Transformation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "engineer = FeatureEngineer(\n",
    "    transformations=[\"changeraw\", \"changepct\"],\n",
    "    entity_column=\"country\",\n",
    "    date_column=\"Date\",\n",
    "    data_columns=[\"SVENY01\", \"SVENY10\"],\n",
    "    verbose=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "df_lib = engineer.fit_transform(df_bbm)\n",
    "df_lib[[\"Date\", \"SVENY01_changeraw\", \"SVENY10_changepct\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 3.3: Comparison with Python Benchmarks"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_manual = df_bbm.copy()\n",
    "df_manual[\"diff01\"] = df_manual[\"SVENY01\"].diff()\n",
    "df_manual[\"pct10\"] = df_manual[\"SVENY10\"].pct_change(fill_method=None)\n",
    "\n",
    "merged = pd.merge(df_lib, df_manual[[\"Date\", \"diff01\", \"pct10\"]], on=\"Date\")\n",
    "merged[[\"Date\", \"SVENY01_changeraw\", \"diff01\", \"SVENY10_changepct\", \"pct10\"]].dropna().head()"
   ]
  }
 ],
